com.pb.locationintelligence.geo911

Interface Geo911Service

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Geo911ServiceImpl

    public interface Geo911Service
    This service provides Life-saving emergency call-routing information (PSAP details) w.r.t requested Address or Latitude-Longitude.

    • Method Detail

      • getPSAPByAddress

        void getPSAPByAddress(android.content.Context context,
                    java.lang.String address,
                    RequestObserver<PsapResponse> requestObserver)
        Retrieves Public Safety Answering Points (PSAP) details. Accepts the address as input and returns PSAP locations' details including agency name, phone number, county name, coverage, contact person's details, site details and mailing address
        Parameters:
        context - Required - Android Context
        address - Required - Free-form address text
        requestObserver - Required - Asynchronous request observer

      • getPSAPByLocation

        void getPSAPByLocation(android.content.Context context,
                     java.lang.Double latitude,
                     java.lang.Double longitude,
                     RequestObserver<PsapResponse> requestObserver)
        Retrieves Public Safety Answering Points (PSAP) details. Accepts latitude and longitude co-ordinates as input and returns PSAP locations' details including agency name, including agency name, phone number, county name, coverage, contact person's details, site details and mailing address.
        Parameters:
        context - Required - Android Context
        latitude - Required - latitude of the location
        longitude - Required - longitude of the location
        requestObserver - Required - Asynchronous request observer
